S3 Durability and scalibility 

               S3 provides upto 99.99999999999 (11nines) durability and that is through storing the data into 3 availibility zones. 
                                                        which is called redundancy.

RULES AND POLICIES 
              S3 name should be unique
              S3 Bucket are regional 
              s3 S3 Object size can be upto 5TB


AWS S3 ACCESS USING CLI

              CLI needs to be authenticated with the AWS account (Go to security creditionals under my account and get the access key)

                                                  Commands 
To test connectivity wwith aws    : - aws sts get-caller-identity 
To list the buckets               : - aws s3 ls
To View content inside the bucket : - aws s3 ls s3:// NAMEOFTHEBUCKET
To Move the content               : - aws s3 mv s3:// NAMEOFTHEsourceBUCKET/OBJECTNAME s3:// NAMEOFTHEdestinationBUCKET 
To View all the content in bucket : - aws s3 ls s3:// NAMEOFTHEBUCKET --recursive


